WEBVTT

00:05:29.240 --> 00:05:33.456
And we actually went out and polled
a thousand individual investors,

00:05:33.480 --> 00:05:35.496
and we found something fascinating.

00:05:35.520 --> 00:05:37.016
Overwhelmingly,

00:05:37.040 --> 00:05:40.656
people wanted to add
those extra words into the formula.

00:05:40.680 --> 00:05:43.736
71 percent of people said yes,

00:05:43.760 --> 00:05:46.336
they were interested
in sustainable investing,

00:05:46.360 --> 00:05:49.296
which we define as taking the best
in class investment process

00:05:49.320 --> 00:05:51.056
that you already have traditionally

00:05:51.080 --> 00:05:53.136
and adding in the extra
information you get

00:05:53.160 --> 00:05:56.416
when you think about the environment
and society and good governance.

00:05:56.440 --> 00:05:58.176
71 percent wanted that.

